@startuml
actor "Batch Scheduler" as Scheduler
participant "BatchConfig" as Config
participant "ItemReader" as Reader
participant "GraphQLClient" as GQLClient
participant "UniversitySystem" as UniSystem

== Student Data Retrieval ==
Scheduler -> Config: Trigger importJob
Config -> Reader: studentReader()
Reader -> GQLClient: getStudents()
GQLClient -> GQLClient: Prepare GraphQL query\n{ students { items { fullName guid ... } } }
GQLClient -> UniSystem: POST /graphql\n{ query: "{ students { items { ... } } }" }
UniSystem -> UniSystem: Process query
UniSystem -> GQLClient: JSON Response\n{ "data": { "students": { "items": [...] } } }
GQLClient -> GQLClient: Parse JSON to StudentsResponse
GQLClient -> Reader: StudentsResponse
Reader -> Config: Iterator<StudentDTO>

== Employee Data Retrieval ==
Config -> Reader: employeeReader()
Reader -> GQLClient: getEmployees()
GQLClient -> GQLClient: Prepare GraphQL query\n{ employees { items { fullName guid ... } } }
GQLClient -> UniSystem: POST /graphql\n{ query: "{ employees { items { ... } } }" }
UniSystem -> UniSystem: Process query
UniSystem -> GQLClient: JSON Response\n{ "data": { "employees": { "items": [...] } } }
GQLClient -> GQLClient: Parse JSON to EmployeesResponse
GQLClient -> Reader: EmployeesResponse
Reader -> Config: Iterator<EmployeeDTO>

@enduml